history.proof: intros. assert (H9: expf (L m zero x y) x_1 y). split. - sfirstorder depth: 3. - hauto lq: on use: nf_L0L1_IIA, nf_L0L1_IIC, nf_L0L1_IIB. - hauto lq: on use: nf_L0L1_IIC, nf_L0L1_IIB, nf_L0L1_IIA.

exceptions.tactic: intros m x y x' y' m1 m2 H1 H2 H3 H4 x_1 y_0 y'0 x'1 y'0b x_1b H5 H6 H7 H8.

original: intros m x y x' y' m1 m2 H1 H2 H3 H4 x_1 y_0 y'0 x'1 y'0b x_1b H5 H6 H7 H8. assert (H9: expf (L m zero x y) x_1 y). { split. apply H5. apply H6. } assert (H10: expf m x' y'0). { split. apply H7. apply H8. } assert (H11: ~ expf (L m zero x y) x' y'0b). { intro. apply H8. apply H10. } assert (H12: expf (L m one x' y') x_1b y). { split. apply H6. apply H7. } contradict H11. apply H3. apply H10. apply H12.
